# Runtime debugging on target

## Common runtime problems

### 1. Library missing

```bash
# On target
ldd /usr/bin/myapp
# Missing: libsomething.so.1
```

**Fix in recipe:**
```bitbake
RDEPENDS:${PN} += "libsomething"
```

### 2. Wrong kernel module

```bash
# Check loaded modules
lsmod
modinfo mydriver
dmesg | grep mydriver
```

**Fix:** Ensure module autoload
```bitbake
KERNEL_MODULE_AUTOLOAD += "mydriver"
```

### 3. Systemd service failing

```bash
systemctl status myservice
journalctl -u myservice
```

**Recipe fix:**
```bitbake
SYSTEMD_SERVICE:${PN} = "myservice.service"
SYSTEMD_AUTO_ENABLE:${PN} = "enable"
```

## Debug toolbelt for target

```bash
# Install debug tools
IMAGE_INSTALL:append = " strace gdb valgrind ltrace"

# Runtime probe
strace -f -o /tmp/trace.log myapp
gdb /usr/bin/myapp core.dump
```

## Boot-time debugging

**Serial console:**
```bash
# In U-Boot
setenv bootargs console=ttyS0,115200 earlyprintk debug
boot
```

**Kernel command line:**
```bash
# In local.conf
APPEND += "debug ignore_loglevel initcall_debug"
```
