   Runtime modification of DT fragments (FPGA, daughterboards).

8. How to reduce kernel boot time?
   CONFIG_CC_OPTIMIZE_FOR_SIZE, initcall debug, async probe.

## Rootfs

9. How to fit rootfs in 8MB flash?
   Busybox, musl libc, dropbear, initramfs, squashfs.

