# Common Problems & Fixes

## 1. Fetch failure

**Error:** `SRC_URI` fails (network/git)

**Fix:**
```bash
# Use mirror
BB_GENERATE_MIRROR_TARBALLS = "1"
BB_ALLOWED_NETWORKS = "git.company.com"

# Or local tarball
SRC_URI = "file://../downloads/mysource.tar.gz"
```

## 2. Compile error

**Error:** Missing headers/libraries

**Fix:**
```bitbake
DEPENDS += "libusb openssl"
# Or add sysroot
CFLAGS:append = " -I${STAGING_INCDIR}/custom"
```

## 3. Runtime library missing

**Error:** `error while loading shared libraries`

**Fix:**
```bitbake
RDEPENDS:${PN} += "libssl"
```

## 4. Kernel module not loading

**Error:** `modprobe: module not found`

**Fix:**
```bitbake
KERNEL_MODULE_AUTOLOAD += "mydriver"
# Check if module built
ls tmp/work/.../kernel-module-mydriver/
```

## 5. Image too large

**Error:** `No space left on device`

**Fix:**
```bitbake
# Remove dev packages
PACKAGE_EXCLUDE = "*-dev"
# Reduce docs
IMAGE_FEATURES:remove = "doc-pkgs"
# Overhead factor
IMAGE_OVERHEAD_FACTOR = "1.0"
```

## 6. Slow builds

**Fix:**
```bitbake
BB_NUMBER_THREADS = "16"
PARALLEL_MAKE = "-j 16"
INHERIT += "ccache"
# Use sstate mirror
SSTATE_MIRRORS = "file://.* http://buildcache.local/sstate/"
```

## 7. sstate hash mismatch

**Fix:**
```bash
bitbake-diffsigs tmp/stamps/*/recipe/task.sigdata.*
# Fix by pinning versions
SRCREV = "${AUTOREV}"  # Bad
SRCREV = "abc123def"   # Good
```

## 8. do_rootfs fails

**Fix:**
```bash
# Manual rootfs creation
bitbake -c cleanall rootfs
bitbake -c rootfs -f rootfs
# Check missing packages
grep "Unable to find package" tmp/work/.../log.do_rootfs
```

## 9. devtool modify fails

**Fix:**
```bash
# Reset
devtool reset myrecipe
# Re-extract
devtool modify myrecipe
# Or use workspace
bitbake -c devshell myrecipe
```

## 10. QEMU boot fails

**Fix:**
```bash
# Add debug
QB_OPT_APPEND = "-serial mon:stdio"
APPEND += "console=ttyS0 debug"
# Check kernel command line
cat /proc/cmdline
```
